suite.doc:
Books Library UI Test Suite
This suite validates the Books Library web application user interface through comprehensive end-to-end browser automation tests. Tests are designed following Gherkin principles and Page Object Model to ensure maintainability and clear business logic representation.
Technology Stack: - Browser Library 19.12.3 (Playwright-based) - Robot Framework 7.4.1 with modern syntax - Chromium headless browser for CI/CD compatibility
